+        // with zero-deposit series, but that self-collision does not itself realize WETH. Positive profit would
+        // require pre-existing third-party value or a nonzero-collateral concurrent operation that shares the same
+        // uncommitted `getNextId()` window; this isolated verifier does not synthesize that extra economic leg.
+        realizedProfit = _wethBalance() > startBalance ? _wethBalance() - startBalance : 0;
